---
import DefaultLayout from "../../layouts/default.astro";
---

<DefaultLayout title="Meter Raja Privacy Policy">
    <div
        class="border-default p-6 mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl tracking-wider justify-around md:p-12"
    >
        <h1 class="mb-4 text-4xl tracking-tight text-heading md:text-6xl">
            Meter Raja Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="font-normal text-body mb-3">Last Updated: 05/12/2025</p>
        <p class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
            Meter Raja (“the App”) is a digital meter application developed and
            owned by StepZero Labs Private Limited (“Company”, “we”, “our”, or
            “us”). This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, disclose,
            and protect your information when you use the Meter Raja app.
        </p>
        <p class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
            By downloading, accessing, or using Meter Raja, you agree to the
            terms of this Privacy Policy.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-3xl mb-2 mt-4">
            1. Information We Collect
        </h2>

        <h3 class="text-heading text-xl mb-2 mt-4">
            1.1 Information You Provide
        </h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Driver Details: Name, phone number, vehicle number,
                permit/registration details (only when required for
                verification).
            </li>

            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Account Credentials: Passwords or PINs you create inside the app
                (stored securely).
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-heading text-xl mb-2 mt-4">
            1.2 Automatically Collected Information
        </h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Location Information: We collect real-time location data while
                the app is running (foreground or background) to calculate
                distance, fares, and provide an accurate digital meter
                experience.
            </li>
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Device Information: Device model, operating system, app version,
                IP address, and diagnostic information.
            </li>
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Usage Data: Actions taken inside the app, ride/meter session
                logs, and crash data.
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-heading text-xl mb-2 mt-4">
            1.3 No Sensitive Personal Data
        </h3>
        <p class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
            We do not collect Aadhar, PAN, financial data, biometric
            information, or any other sensitive documents.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-2xl mb-2 mt-4">
            2. How We Use Your Information
        </h2>

        <p class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
            We use the collected information to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Accurately calculate distance, time, and fares.
            </li>
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Display trip logs and meter readings.
            </li>

            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Improve app accuracy, performance, and security.
            </li>

            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Provide customer support and resolve issues.
            </li>
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Prevent fraud, misuse, and ensure compliance with local
                transport regulations.
            </li>
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Generate analytics to improve service quality (aggregated and
                anonymized).
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
            We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-2xl mb-2 mt-4">3. Location Data Usage</h2>

        <p class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
            Meter Raja requires precise location access to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Calculate trip distance
            </li>
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Show live meter readings
            </li>
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Log ride routes for transparency and record-keeping
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
            Location data is collected only during active meter sessions and is
            not used for marketing.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-2xl mb-2 mt-4">
            4. Sharing of Information
        </h2>

        <p class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
            We may share information only in the following cases:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Service Providers: For analytics, crash reporting, and backend
                hosting (e.g., Firebase, AWS).
            </li>
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Legal Compliance: If required by law, courts, or government
                authorities.
            </li>
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Business Transfers: In the event of a merger, acquisition, or
                restructuring of StepZero Labs Private Limited.
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
            We never share personal information with advertisers or marketing
            platforms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-2xl mb-2 mt-4">
            5. Data Storage & Security
        </h2>

        <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Data is stored securely on encrypted servers managed by StepZero
                Labs or trusted cloud providers.
            </li>
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                We implement industry-standard security measures including
                encryption, secure servers, and access controls.
            </li>
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                While we take strong precautions, no system is completely
                secure.
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-2xl mb-2 mt-4">6. Data Retention</h2>

        <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Trip logs, meter data, and driver details are retained as long
                as your account is active.
            </li>
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                You may request deletion of your data anytime (see Section 9).
            </li>
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Some data may be retained if required by law.
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-2xl mb-2 mt-4">7. Children’s Privacy</h2>

        <p class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
            Meter Raja is intended for adults who operate taxis or autos. We do
            not knowingly collect data from children under 18.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-2xl mb-2 mt-4">8. Third-Party Links</h2>

        <p class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
            The app does not contain third-party ads or links. If any external
            links are added later, we will update this policy.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-2xl mb-2 mt-4">9. Your Rights</h2>

        <p class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">You may:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Request access to your data
            </li>
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Request correction of inaccurate details
            </li>
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Request deletion of your account and related data
            </li>
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Withdraw permissions (such as location access)
            </li>
            <li class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
                Contact us for privacy-related queries
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
            To exercise these rights, email us at:
            <a href="mailto:hello@naviget.in">hello@naviget.in</a>
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-2xl mb-2 mt-4">
            10. Changes to This Privacy Policy
        </h2>

        <p class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
            We may update this policy occasionally. Continued use of the app
            after changes means you accept the updated policy.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-2xl mb-2 mt-4">11. Contact Us</h2>

        <p class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
            For any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy,
            contact:
        </p>

        <p class="md:text-lg font-normal text-body">
            StepZero Labs Private Limited <br />
            Email: <a href="mailto:hello@naviget.in">hello@naviget.in</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</DefaultLayout>
